---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Navbar from "../components/Navbar.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy">
  <Navbar />
  
  <main class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-6 py-16 lg:px-8 lg:py-24">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-ink sm:text-5xl mb-12">Privacy Policy</h1>
    
    <div class="prose prose-vercel text-body leading-relaxed space-y-8">
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-ink mb-4">Our Commitment</h2>
        <p>
          At Image Tool Stack, privacy is not just a feature; it is our foundation. Most online image tools upload your files to a remote server for processing. 
          We believe your private images should stay private.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-ink mb-4">Browser-Based Processing</h2>
        <p>
          Unlike our competitors, we utilize modern browser APIs (like Canvas and WebAssembly) to process your images locally on your device. 
          <strong>Your files are never uploaded to our servers.</strong>
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-ink mb-4">Data Collection</h2>
        <p>
          We do not collect personal information. We use anonymous analytics to understand site usage and improve our tools, 
          but this never includes any data from the images you process.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-ink mb-4">Cookies</h2>
        <p>
          We use minimal cookies for essential site functionality and basic analytics. You can disable these in your browser settings at any time.
        </p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</Layout>
